title: 'Genuine slim fit jeans!'
body: Absolutely genuine Levi's. I know, as have been wearing only Levi's jeans since 15 years. This is slim fit not skinny. So if you slightly loose, this is the one. Not stretchable, but not required also, as it's not skinny.
